plot: Cosmo and Wanda spend the night at Chloe's, disguised as Flightless Booby Birds. But when Chloe's parents decide to return the boobies to their natural habitat in the rainforest, Timmy and Chloe have to go and save them.

Chloe decides to disguise Cosmo and Wanda as her pet blue-footed boobies, but Chloe's parents take Cosmo and Wanda back to the forest to return them to their natural habitat. So now, Timmy and Chloe must find Cosmo and Wanda before they get into any real danger.—DeJon Diaz
